ective nuclei get maximized due to the\nnoncollinear secular hyperfine interaction with a resident electron in the QD.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2011 07:39:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 May 2012 11:54:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-05-02"}
